235
00:15:30,703 --> 00:15:34,107
Tak ada sampanye karena barang-barangmu
belum tiba.

236
00:15:35,142 --> 00:15:36,293
Apa?

237
00:15:36,843 --> 00:15:39,105
Kenapa mereka belum tiba?

238
00:15:39,483 --> 00:15:41,745
Apa mereka bermalasan di tempat lain?

239
00:15:42,223 --> 00:15:45,282
Kenapa kita tak minum anggur beras
