240
00:15:45,552 --> 00:15:46,967
Ayo kita mengingat masa lalu kita.

241
00:15:50,392 --> 00:15:53,018
Barusan kubilang, jangan bicarakan masa itu.

242
00:15:54,762 --> 00:15:56,985
Kau lupa apa yang baru saja kukatakan.

243
00:15:59,333 --> 00:16:00,585
Kim Seonbae.

244
00:16:01,172 --> 00:16:03,597
Mungkin itu karena kau lupa

245
00:16:04,142 --> 00:16:06,536
