299
00:20:11,652 --> 00:20:12,803
Maaf.

300
00:20:48,422 --> 00:20:49,604
Apa kau manusia?

301
00:20:51,063 --> 00:20:52,607
Apa aku terlihat seperti hantu?

302
00:20:53,432 --> 00:20:54,675
Siapa?

